title: He's Our Type of Man
itunes:title: He's Our Type of Man
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I have been dating my boyfriend for the past 4 months and I thought things were getting serious with us, so I told my brother about him. My brother and I are close in age and he always gives great advice on my relationships. My brother wanted to see my new boyfriend, so I gave him my phone and let him swipe to see a few of my boyfriend’s most recent pictures...................
